[06/08/2017 07:33:22] <font color="#ffff00">Nodis negros, charranes,</font>
[06/08/2017 07:33:22] <font color="#ffff00">alcatraces,...</font>
[06/08/2017 07:33:26] <font color="#ffff00">...estas aves marinas se alimentan</font>
[06/08/2017 07:33:26] <font color="#ffff00">de los mismos pececillos...</font>
[06/08/2017 07:33:28] <font color="#ffff00">...que los mahi mahi.</font>
